data.description:
****PRICE REDUCTION****
Amazing Spacious 2,147 sqft Single-Level Home. This Home Has Three Bedrooms And Two Bathrooms, Offering Ample Space For Comfortable Living. It Also Features A Formal Dining Room And Two Separate Living Rooms, Providing Versatility For Various Activities And Gatherings.
Inside, You'll Notice The Tasteful Upgrades, Including Stylish Tile Floors (Brand-new A/C HVAC 2022) And Plush Carpeting. The Kitchen Is A Highlight, Boasting Vaulted Ceilings And Plenty Of Room For culinary Adventures.
Located In The Heart Of Buckeye, Arizona, This Home Enjoys A Prime Location, Just A Short Walk From An Elementary School, Making It Convenient For Families. Outside, The Backyard Offers A Welcoming Patio And Low-Maintenance Synthetic Grass, Perfect For Outdoor Enjoyment. This home combines size, style, and an excellent location, making it an attractive choice for comfortable living.
